        "name": "Talmandor's Shout",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "After seeing an enemy harm one of your allies, you deliver a righteous shout in the name of the celestial Talmandor. Attempt an Intimidation check to Demoralize, comparing the result to the Will DC of each enemy within a 60-foot emanation; this Demoralize attempt doesn\u2019t take any penalty for not sharing a language. It\u2019s possible to get a different degree of success for each target.",
